# Asset hygiene (logos/icons/images)

- Store icons in `src/assets/icons/*` and images/logos in `src/assets/images/*`.
- Prefer importing assets via the barrel files:
  - `src/assets/icons/index.js`
  - `src/assets/images/index.js`
- Avoid ad-hoc string paths to assets from JSX when a module import works.

## Repo references (examples)
- Logos: `src/assets/images/header-logo.svg` (barrel: `headerLogo`)
- Nav logo usage: `src/components/Nav.jsx`
- Social icons data: `src/constants/index.js` (`footerSocialLinks`)

## Filenames and diffs
- Prefer keeping existing filenames if it reduces changes (swap the file contents instead).
- If filenames must change, update barrel exports and all imports consistently.

## Reporting
Include an **Assets** section in the summary:
- added/removed/renamed files
- where each asset is used (section/component)
